<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;">OnBootSec</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">=1min             </span><span style="--shiki-light:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#6A737D;"># 系统启动后 1 分钟首次执行</span></span>
